OL,3,CCardiff Rugby takeover by Ospreys
OL,4,Cowners falls through
OL,6,FA proposed takeover of Cardiff by
OL,7,FOspreys owners Y11 Sport and Media has
OL,8,Ffallen through, the Welsh Rugby Union
OL,9,Fhas confirmed.
OL,11,FThe future of the Ospreys had been
OL,12,Fplunged into uncertainty after Y11
OL,13,Femerged as the preferred bidders to
OL,14,Fpurchase Cardiff from the WRU.
OL,16,FAmid WRU plans to cut one of its four
OL,17,Fmen's regional sides, four-time league
OL,18,Fchampions Ospreys have only been given
OL,19,Fguarantees as a professional team
OL,20,Funtil June 2027.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
