OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776874270
OL,3,CCardiff Rugby takeover by Ospreys
OL,4,Cowners falls through
OL,6,FHowever, an announcement on Wednesday
OL,7,Fconfirmed the WRU and Y11 have
OL,8,F"jointly agreed" that the Ospreys'
OL,9,Fowners would "withdraw from the bid
OL,10,Fprocess" due "to constructive
OL,11,Fdiscussions" and that Cardiff will
OL,12,Fremain under WRU ownership "for now
OL,13,Fand until it makes commercial and
OL,14,Fstrategic sense to revisit this
OL,15,Fdecision".
