OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776874270
OL,3,CCardiff Rugby takeover by Ospreys
OL,4,Cowners falls through
OL,6,FHowever, the WRU reaffirmed their
OL,7,Fdesire to press ahead with their
OL,8,Fcontroversial "Way Forward" strategy,
OL,9,Fwhich will reduce the number of
OL,10,Fprofessional clubs in Wales from four
OL,11,Fto three by the end of the 2027/28
OL,12,Fseason.
OL,14,FThe decision to move forward cutting
OL,15,Fthe number of professional teams in
OL,16,FWales comes after the WRU Chair,
OL,17,FRichard Collier-Keywood, resigned in
OL,18,FMarch ahead of a no confidence vote in
OL,19,Fhis leadership.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
