OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776874270
OL,3,CCardiff Rugby takeover by Ospreys
OL,4,Cowners falls through
OL,6,FA decision on the process of
OL,7,Fdownsizing will be decided in June.
OL,9,FIn a statement the WRU CEO Abi Tierney
OL,10,Fsaid: "We know we need to move to
OL,11,Fthree clubs, nothing has changed
OL,12,Fthere, for both financial and
OL,13,Fperformance reasons and so we can
OL,14,Finvest in the right way in our pathway
OL,15,Fto ensure the future of the game,"
OL,17,F"But this move brings stability to the
OL,18,Fsystem where it is needed and a
OL,19,Fcalmness and assuredness to our plans
OL,20,Ffor the future.
OL,26,@rD@GOUwD@bO]yD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
