PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776874270
OL,3,CCardiff Rugby takeover by Ospreys
OL,4,Cowners falls through
OL,6,F"Y11 presented the best bid for
OL,7,FCardiff Rugby but the WRU has
OL,8,Fultimately concluded that it is in the
OL,9,Fbest interests of Welsh rugby for
OL,10,FCardiff Rugby to remain under WRU
OL,11,Fownership for now.
OL,13,F"We remain undeterred from our
OL,14,Fambition to move to three professional
OL,15,Fsides, this is necessary for the
OL,16,Ffuture of our game.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
