PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776874270
OL,3,CCardiff Rugby takeover by Ospreys
OL,4,Cowners falls through
OL,6,F"We will continue to invest the #28m
OL,7,Fwe have earmarked for our pathways
OL,8,Fover the next five years, in a phased
OL,9,Fway, and we retain our ambitions for
OL,10,Fcommercial growth in the professional
OL,11,Fgame.
OL,13,F"I would like to add that we are all
OL,14,Fvery grateful to Y11 for the
OL,15,Fprofessionalism and commitment to
OL,16,FWelsh rugby they have displayed
OL,17,Fthroughout this process.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
