OL,3,CCardiff Rugby takeover by Ospreys
OL,4,Cowners falls through
OL,6,FY11 Sport & Media spokesperson said
OL,7,F:"PRA25 for the Ospreys and top tier
OL,8,Frugby in Swansea, partnering with
OL,9,FSwansea Council and developing St
OL,10,FHelens is the right outcome, whilst
OL,11,Fcontinuing to work with the WRU to
OL,12,Ffurther build a better pro rugby
OL,13,Fenvironment.
OL,15,F"We are grateful to the WRU for their
OL,16,Fopenness and transparency throughout
OL,17,Fthe negotiation period.
OL,26,@oD@BOUwD@AOU
