OL,3,CCardiff Rugby takeover by Ospreys
OL,4,Cowners falls through
OL,6,F"Thank you to the Ospreys supporters
OL,7,Ffor their patience and understanding,
OL,8,Fwe know these have been worrying times
OL,9,Ffor fans."
OL,11,FThe PRB chair Marianne Okland said:
OL,12,F"This decision will hopefully
OL,13,Fcontribute towards stability to the
OL,14,Fsystem in Wales.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@JO]sD@XottD@AOU
