OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776874270
OL,3,CCardiff Rugby takeover by Ospreys
OL,4,Cowners falls through
OL,6,F"It's good to see that the WRU Board
OL,7,Fhas kept an open mind and evolved its
OL,8,Fthinking in line with developments.
OL,9,FWelsh rugby now have an opportunity to
OL,10,Fwork together to create a sustainable
OL,11,Ffuture for the whole game in Wales
OL,12,Fwhich is a priority for us all."
